Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.83,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur2}"In the Bluest Sky, I Can Meet With You"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:34.87,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}I felt a signal pass through me today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.25,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}As I went out to meet up with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:45.67,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}In this crowded cityscape, an enlightening wind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.93,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}Is blowing hard into my face
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:59.15,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}Up in the clouds, above the Earth,\Nwhere the Angels' ladders reach with grace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:05.44,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}I stretched out my arms, and climbed right on.  Now I can go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:10.11,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}Everywhere, gently riding a white wispy cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.66,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}In the bluest sky, I can meet with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:20.83,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}No matter what the time, where the place\NThe path to take, I want to see it through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:25.51,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}I will never give up until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:31.85,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}I want to gather up all pieces of the dreams\Nthat shine with seven rainbow colors
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:36.85,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}Ahh… perhaps the answers that I want
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:42.56,English Songs Translation [1],,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1\blur2}Are there all along in front of me
